1. Get a YG vagrant environment up.  See
https://yougov.kilnhg.com/Code/Repositories/Systems/yg-app-base-image/Files/README.md?rev=tip.
SSH into it, and 'cd /vagrant/mettle'.

2. Run ./dbsetup.sh

3. mkvirtualenv mettle

4. pip install -r dev_requirements.txt

5. Install Node.js into the virtualenv:

  nodeenv -p --prebuilt

6. Install JS tools into the virtualenv:

  npm install -g react-tools bower

7. Install frontend JS/CSS packages into the mettle/static/ folder:

  cd mettle/static
  bower install
